<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><refentry version="5.0-subset Scilab" xml:id="camget" xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><refnamediv><refname>camget</refname><refpurpose>Get a property from an opened camera.</refpurpose></refnamediv><refsynopsisdiv><title>Syntax</title><synopsis>value = camget(handle, prop)</synopsis></refsynopsisdiv><refsection><title>Description</title><para><function>camget</function> reads OpenCV camera capture properties by numeric id or by name.</para></refsection><refsection><title>Examples</title><programlisting><![CDATA[n = camopen(0);
